Jagris waited patiently, listening to the hiss of static coming from 
her comlink. If she was back on Cybertron, none of this would be 
happening. Didn't anyone know these pods had a limited air supply? 
She'd go offline soon if someone didn't come. 

"This is Lieutenant Jagris of the Cybertron Special Forces... somebot 
answer me!!" 

*Did they forget? I can't bust outta here myself! Or...* 

Jagris put her feet to the lid of the pod, and pushed as hard as she 
could in such tight quarters.
